data.description: COME HOME TO THE COUNTRY!  This peaceful home features gorgeous views out every window.  Located on a tree-filled small acreage tract, it is ready to be called your own!  Numerous cosmetic and system updates have been made including new water well pump and pressure tank (2023), new septic system (2022), new layout, paint, flooring, covered livestock shed, fencing, and bonus area remodel which offers potential for a fourth bedroom, office, or to suit your specific needs.  If you've been looking for a small homestead to call your own that's ready for your 4H projects, chickens, or horses, this may be the place!  There is room to expand here. Offering close proximity to Lake Somerville and a just a ten-minute scenic drive into the town of Burton!
